<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-275] Document RPCs for getattr</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-275</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The shell command &apos;stat&apos; issues a POSIX system call &apos;stat()&apos; which results in a call to &apos;ll_getattr()&apos; in lustre/llite/file.c. &lt;br/&gt;
Document the messages exchanged to carry out this operation as well as any state change that it can cause.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
